short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tracks the URLs of tabs opened in the current window.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tab Tracker is a simple and powerful Chrome extension that helps you manage your browsing sessions efficiently. With just one click, you can view, copy, and save the URLs of all open tabs in your current window and share it with others.

v1.2 update - 

Group URLs by domain for better organization.
Select multiple URLs and copy them with a single click.
Easily copy individual URLs by simply clicking on them.
